title: Talking to Durianrider directly: the criminal charges are real, the court case is real.
description: I keep telling people that I'm not a nice guy… but seriously… given what I've been through with this guy (and the damage he's done to veganism as a movement, not to mention myself, personally, and so many other people) how much nicer could I possibly have been in this scenario?
